      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5633328038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "前の夏フェスの時はダイエットですっごく\n苦労しましたけど、今回は気が楽なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really struggled with dieting at the last summer festival‚\nbut this time it’s easier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2966661372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8633328038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、別に開き直って\n暴飲暴食してた訳じゃないですからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ but that doesn’t mean\nI was being reckless and overeating‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8966661372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "疑ってないから大丈夫だよ\nさあ、もうじき出番だ。楽しみにしてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not suspecting anything‚ it’s fine.\nAlright‚ you’re up soon. I’m looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.466667803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.6266679046
    },
    {
