    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、次で最後の曲……って、え、え、え！？\nなになに、急にみんなどうしたの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ the next song is the last… Wait‚ what‚ what!?\nWhat‚ what‚ what’s going on‚ everyone!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0266695576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9933346984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "……誕生日、おめでとう？\nわっ！　おっきな桃のケーキ！　美味しそ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Happy… birthday?\nWoah! A huge peach cake! It looks so good~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9600013651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3600013651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "え、え！？　みんな一斉にうちわを出して……\nって、あれ？　これって私のメンバーカラー……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ eh!? Everyone’s holding up handy fans…\nW-Wait? Is this… my member color…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9266680317,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5000.001780200002,
          "startTime": 62.9266698119
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9266680317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃の誕生日を祝った時のように、パンフレットに）\n（挟み込みをした。今回はチラシではなくうちわだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Like when we celebrated Kotono’s birthday‚ I had it）\n（inserted. This time‚ it’s handy fans instead of flyers.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333335796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（片面にはサプライズの内容を書いておき、そして）\n（もう片面は渚のメンバーカラーで染めている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wrote the surprise message on one side‚ and）\n（colored the other side with Nagisa’s member color.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0000002462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5932686087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……みんな、ありがとうございます\nえへへ、嬉し過ぎてなんだかふわふわしちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… Thank you‚ everyone.\nEhehe‚ I’m so happy I feel like I’m floating…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1599352754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8265871919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって月ストとファンのみなさんにお祝いして\nもらえて、私……とっても幸せです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m… so happy to be celebrated like this\nby Moon Tempest and all the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6932538585,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
