    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ、無事に終わって良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad the live show ended without a hitch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8599098439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "渚へのサプライズも成功して良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad the surprise for Nagisa was a success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8599098439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.2892976517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの様子がずっとおかしかった理由が\n分かって安心しましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m relieved to know why\nKotono-chan was acting so strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.722630985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズに挑むのが琴乃ちゃんだけ\n初めてだったから、ずっと緊張してたみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like she was nervous because it was her\nfirst time trying to pull off a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.322630985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.9226289505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……{user}さんも\nなかなかでしたよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but… you were pretty good too‚\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8559622838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.6892956172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なかなかって……何が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Pretty good… What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6892956172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "私が琴乃ちゃんを心配してる時\nずーっと様子がおかしかったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was worried about Kotono-chan‚\nyou were acting really strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7476628536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はは……バレないで済んだだけ良しとしてくれ",
      "translations": {
